          1,
          "DARQ "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "is a dark and somewhat twisted game that manages to be scary in oh so subtle ways. Traverse puzzles by bending reality as you walk up walls, rotate your dreamscape 360 degrees and avoid monsters as you try to wake up from an eternal nightmare. Are you afraid of the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "DARQ"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "? You will be after you make your way through this Tim Burton-esque adventure."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
