      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The enemies look like actors in a haunted house attraction: stoic and lurching. The aesthetics are an odd combination when you take the core concept into consideration but this game as a whole is wonderfully weird. Collecting severed arms to progress is just one of the morbid aspects of "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "DARQ"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " and the quirky little surprises are what makes this game great. "
        ]
      ]
